  <data name="labelInstructions.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>REMINDER:
Your Camera Sensitivity in
Roblox must be 0.84 on a 125%
and 0.68 on a 100% scaled
display for AutoCam to function
correctly!

Use shift-lock or first person for
reaping and sowing.

Be in third person WITHOUT
shift-lock for Idling.
AutoInvite sends a mass village
invite after the progress bar is
filled AND when you start Idling.

Be in first person for mixing.
Mixing mode only works if you
start bowl 4 or 5!</value>
